87
00:09:02,333 --> 00:09:05,458
I may be immortal, but I'm weak.

88
00:09:06,625 --> 00:09:09,583
If you're ever in trouble, I'll help you.

89
00:09:09,583 --> 00:09:11,917
That's what brothers are for!

90
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,208
Fu...

91
00:09:26,933 --> 00:09:29,642
