115
00:12:11,042 --> 00:12:12,375
Don't worry.

116
00:12:12,375 --> 00:12:16,250
They'll come... and save us...

117
00:12:17,083 --> 00:12:21,208
Gugu, don't overexert yourself.

118
00:12:21,208 --> 00:12:24,042
Flower...

119
00:12:33,667 --> 00:12:37,167
To... Tomorrow... I'll buy you another flower...

120
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,667
It'll be all right.

121
00:12:42,125 --> 00:12:44,833
No, Gugu.

122
00:12:44,833 --> 00:12:47,375
Let's go pick it ourselves.

123
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:57,417
I know of only one place
where this flower blooms.

124
00:12:57,417 --> 00:12:59,625
You know of it too, right, Gugu?

125
00:13:02,708 --> 00:13:09,042
Of course... We'll definitely go together...

126
00:13:26,125 --> 00:13:27,667
Rynn...

127
00:13:28,458 --> 00:13:30,292
I love you...

128
00:14:40,708 --> 00:14:43,333
No... It can't be!

129
00:14:44,167 --> 00:14:46,417
Gugu isn't dead!

130
00:14:46,417 --> 00:14:48,750
Gugu isn't dead!

131
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:54,500
He isn't dead!

132
00:15:49,917 --> 00:15:51,917
It escaped.

133
00:15:51,917 --> 00:15:54,292
It heads to the west.

134
00:15:54,292 --> 00:15:55,958
You must go after it.

135
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:58,833
Lift this rock!

136
00:16:00,125 --> 00:16:02,708
