171
00:19:40,625 --> 00:19:45,083
It was the very epitome of happiness.

172
00:19:45,083 --> 00:19:47,542
But something was missing.

173
00:19:47,542 --> 00:19:51,833
And now I see that. It was my true self.

174
00:19:54,875 --> 00:19:56,208
Fushi...

175
00:19:56,208 --> 00:19:59,833
I have no regrets.

176
00:20:08,958 --> 00:20:10,583
