189
00:21:28,125 --> 00:21:35,042
He was a brave... and wonderful person.

190
00:21:44,792 --> 00:21:48,833
Come, Gugu. Leave the rest to us.

191
00:21:48,833 --> 00:21:51,750
You need to be going soon, right?

192
00:21:52,667 --> 00:21:56,042
Ah... yes. That's right.

193
00:21:57,500 --> 00:22:00,250
