194
00:22:00,250 --> 00:22:04,125
Um, well... Shopping.

195
00:22:04,125 --> 00:22:07,000
I... I'll go too. I'll help you.

196
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:09,333
Don't worry, Rynn. He'll be fine on his own.

197
00:22:09,333 --> 00:22:12,333
