203
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:42,292
Oh, that's right. 
I have something to return to you.

204
00:22:42,292 --> 00:22:45,875
Here. Your brother asked me to return it to you.

205
00:22:45,875 --> 00:22:47,833
Remember it?

206
00:22:50,125 --> 00:22:51,875
You should keep it.

207
00:22:51,875 --> 00:22:53,958
It'll remind you of Gu...

208
00:22:53,958 --> 00:22:57,042
Of me.

209
00:22:59,458 --> 00:23:02,292
