212
00:23:12,833 --> 00:23:15,000
Be careful out there.

213
00:23:17,167 --> 00:23:18,833
Thank you...

214
00:23:39,250 --> 00:23:40,833
Rynn!

215
00:23:41,500 --> 00:23:44,833
Rynn! We've been looking all over for you!

216
00:23:44,833 --> 00:23:47,833
